{ A very nice double rook sacrifice. } 15... f6
{ 15...Qxh1+  16.Kd2  Qxa1   16...Qg2  17.Qe5+  Kd8  18.Ng5 !  is immediately decisive.  17.Qe5+  Kd8  18.Qxh8  Ke8   18...Qxb2+  19.Ke1 !  Qc1+  20.Kf2  and Black is out of checks.  19.Qe5+  Kd8  20.Ng5 !  Qxa2  21.c4 !  and Black is powerless against the threat of Nxf7#. }
16. Qxf5 Qxh1+ 17. Kd2 Qxa1 18. Qg6+ Kd8 19. Qxf6+ Ke8 20. Qe5+ Kf7
{ 20...Kd8  21.Qxh8!  Qxb2+  22.Ke1  and White has a winning attack while his king will be safe on f2. }
21. Bc4+ { With mate in a few moves. } *

